              "text": "Mwuhahahaha!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Question option",
      "sections": [],
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "lines": [
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Hey, Head?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "What?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "How did you die?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "I stuck my neck out for an old friend."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "You shouldn't get so cut up about it."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Well if I keep it all bottled up I'll turn into a total head case."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Hey, Head?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "What?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What is your name?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Mumblemumblemumble..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What was that?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "My name is Edward Cranium."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Edd Cranium?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Hahahahahahahahahahaha!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Har har..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Hey Head?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "What now?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Can you do any tricks?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Not any more..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "How come?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Because I used to be able to do a handstand for over an hour while juggling cannon balls with my feet..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Wow, you were quite the entertainer."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Yep. Now I can barely roll my eyes..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I know what you can do!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "What?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Vent..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Don't even suggest it!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Ok."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Hey, Head?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Can't I rest in peace?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "No!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Would you like a new hat?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "No, but could you screw a handle into the top of my head?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "A handle? Why?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Because currently you wave me about by my hair, and it hurts!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Hey, Head?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Will you ever leave me alone?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "No!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Want to go scare some people?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Let's leave it for now."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "All right..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "We'll quit while we're ahead!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "If I try really hard I might be able to will myself deader..."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Using zombie head on Dr Fenkenstrain during Creature of Fenkenstrain",
      "sections": [],
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "lines": [
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I have a winner for you here, Doctor! Look! It's still moving!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Zombie Head",
              "text": "Nobody knows the troubles I've seen...nobody knows my sorrow..."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Dr Fenkenstrain",
              "text": "I can't use that head!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "Why not?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Dr Fenkenstrain",
              "text": "If that thing keeps wriggling around, I'll never get the stitches straight."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Dr Fenkenstrain",
              "text": "...And who knows what problems will come up if we have an undead head on a truly dead body."
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Dr Fenkenstrain",
              "text": "Bring me another head, one that isn't still moving"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}